if it is graphical
  and not in tmux
        the visual is gvimd
if it is not graphical or is tmux
    the visual is vimd

==============
If it is not in tmux
    if there is no session
        set to use xterm
    if no session and does not have arguments
        just start the cli server
    else
        load silent on cli server
If it is in tmux
    if there is no session set to split window
    if it does not have arguments
        just start the tmx server
    if it has arguments
        load silent on tmx server

